ads.ui.admin.guide.title_quick=§lQuick Start
ads.ui.admin.guide.body_quick=§a§lRecommended Flow§r\n\n§f1. Create Quest\n§7Choose a clear name, short description, category, and type.\n\n§f2. Set Target\n§7Use exact IDs like minecraft:zombie or minecraft:diamond_ore.\n\n§f3. Set Required Amount\n§7Keep early quests small so players understand the system.\n\n§f4. Add Points and Rewards\n§7Points always work. Commands are optional and run after completion.\n\n§f5. Test in Player Mode\n§7Use Player Mode from the admin menu before publishing many quests.
ads.ui.admin.guide.title_blocks=§lBlocks, Items & Crafting
ads.ui.admin.guide.body_blocks=§b§lBlock Quest§r\n§7Target: minecraft:stone\n§7Tracks blocks broken.\n\n§a§lPlace Quest§r\n§7Target: minecraft:oak_planks\n§7Tracks blocks placed.\n\n§6§lGather Quest§r\n§7Target: minecraft:apple\n§7Tracks item gains in inventory.\n\n§e§lCraft Quest§r\n§7Target: minecraft:crafting_table\n§7Tracks crafted items when detected by the script.\n\n§fUse exact identifiers. Custom addon IDs work when the item/block exists.
ads.ui.admin.guide.title_combat=§lCombat & Deaths
ads.ui.admin.guide.body_combat=§c§lKill Quest§r\n§7Target: minecraft:zombie\n§7Required amount: number of kills.\n\n§4§lBoss or Custom Mob§r\n§7Target: custom_addon:boss_id\n§7Use the entity type ID from the addon.\n\n§8§lDeath Quest§r\n§7Type: death\n§7Target can be left blank. Required amount controls death count.\n\n§fKeep combat rewards higher than simple gather quests because risk is higher.
ads.ui.admin.guide.title_travel=§lTravel & Routes
ads.ui.admin.guide.body_travel=§a§lVisit Quest§r\n§7Target format: x,y,z\n§7Example: 100,64,100\n§7Completes when player is within 5 blocks.\n\n§2§lWalk Quest§r\n§7Target format: x,y,z;x,y,z;x,y,z\n\n§fAvoid placing targets inside walls.
ads.ui.admin.guide.title_rewards=§lRewards & Shop
ads.ui.admin.guide.body_rewards=§6§lReward Commands§r\n§7Separate multiple commands with semicolons.\n\n§fShop items should cost more than one easy quest.
ads.ui.admin.guide.title_chains=§lChains & Progression
ads.ui.admin.guide.body_chains=§d§lQuest Chains§r\n§7Chains turn separate quests into ordered storylines.
ads.ui.admin.guide.title_tools=§lAdmin Tools
ads.ui.admin.guide.body_tools=§5§lAdmin Dashboard§r\n§7Shows quest counts, player activity, points.
